  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144950/extras/8296ba9a08e25cd076425c56e5764cae.poster.avif?t=1773344180\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144950/extras/8296ba9a08e25cd076425c56e5764cae.webm?t=1773344180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144950/extras/8296ba9a08e25cd076425c56e5764cae.mp4?t=1773344180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect quadrillion of coins, hatch pets to mine for you, and unlock 100 unique hand-crafted areas!<br>An incremental clicker/idle creatures-collection adventure.<br>Dopamine heaven has arrived!</strong></h2><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mine coins (yes, it's as fun as it looks)!<br></li><li>Unlock a huge variety of hand-crafted areas!<br></li><li>Hatch new pets to automatically mine coins for you!<br></li><li>Collect the rarest pets and discover rare variations like Gold, Rainbow, Mega, and Omega!<br></li><li>Tons of random events to make mining exciting, from ice cubes to dragons - anything is possible!<br></li><li>Find, buy, and craft many upgrades for you and your pets!<br></li><li>Ascend every 25 areas to become even stronger!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144950/extras/8296ba9a08e25cd076425c56e5764cae.poster.avif?t=1773344180\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144950/extras/8296ba9a08e25cd076425c56e5764cae.webm?t=1773344180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3144950/extras/8296ba9a08e25cd076425c56e5764cae.mp4?t=1773344180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collect quadrillion of coins, hatch pets to mine for you, and unlock 100 unique hand-crafted areas!<br>An incremental clicker/idle creatures-collection adventure.<br>Dopamine heaven has arrived!</strong></h2><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Mine coins (yes, it's as fun as it looks)!<br></li><li>Unlock a huge variety of hand-crafted areas!<br></li><li>Hatch new pets to automatically mine coins for you!<br></li><li>Collect the rarest pets and discover rare variations like Gold, Rainbow, Mega, and Omega!<br></li><li>Tons of random events to make mining exciting, from ice cubes to dragons - anything is possible!<br></li><li>Find, buy, and craft many upgrades for you and your pets!<br></li><li>Ascend every 25 areas to become even stronger!</li></ul>",
